      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i walk into the kitchen and i still expect to hear him making coffee or complaining about the weather. then i realize it's just me. it's just me in this house every single day and i don't even know why i'm botherng to wake up anymore. everything feels... pointless. like i'm just going through the motions of a life that ended when he did.",
